-- Lonmin Miners to Protest Over Mineworker Death Tomorrow, Labor Union Says
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2010-10-12T12:15:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/lonmin-miners-to-protest-over-mineworker-death-tomorrow-labor-union-says.html
More than 4,000 workers willl stop
working tomorrow at the Rustenburg operations of Lonmin Plc in
South Africa to protest against the death of a worker in an
accident, the National Union of Mineworkers, a labor union, said
in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
